<plot>A burly man lives with his cat in a flat on a busy city street. He sits at his table making origami figures. He decides he's had too much of noise and pollution, so he goes outside and begins to grab human objects, such as cars and houses and planes, and he refolds them into animals and trees. Soon, the landscape is resplendent: what should the man do with himself?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?422604</url></doc>
